  <description>
    <p>**This app is only available in Arabic.**</p>
    <p>
      A simple open-source Quran reader
      
      Features:
    </p>
    <ul>
      <li>Clean Arabic interface</li>
      <li>Automatic light/dark theme</li>
      <li>Fast search functionality</li>
      <li>Customizable font size</li>
      <li>Remembers your exact reading position</li>
      <li>Open-source, ad-free, and lightweight</li>
    </ul>
    <p>
      Focus on what matters - reading the Holy Quran.
    </p>
